OL,6,FChannel Islanders are being left out
OL,7,Fof pocket by disputes raised against
OL,8,Frequests they have made to claim back
OL,9,Fmoney from the collapsed airline Blue
OL,10,FIslands.
OL,12,FBlue Islands ceased operations in
OL,13,FNovember after serving the Channel
OL,14,FIslands for 26 years under different
OL,15,Fnames.
