OL,3,CBanks disputing Blue Islands refund
OL,4,Cpayments, experts claim
OL,6,FIn November, islanders were told to
OL,7,Fcontact their credit or debit card
OL,8,Fprovider with proof of payment and a
OL,9,Fletter of evidence from the Civil
OL,10,FAviation Authority confirming the
OL,11,Fairline had gone into liquidation to
OL,12,Fclaim back money spent on bookings.
OL,14,FMany islanders have already received
OL,15,Ffull refunds, but others are confused
OL,16,Fas to why their refunds are now being
OL,17,Fchallenged.
