OL,3,CBanks disputing Blue Islands refund
OL,4,Cpayments, experts claim
OL,6,FTyler Johnson paid around #200 for
OL,7,Fflight tickets, but after being told
OL,8,Fby his bank that he would receive a
OL,9,Ffull refund, the transaction is now
OL,10,Fbeing disputed, confusingly challenged
OL,11,Fby Blue Islands itself.
OL,13,F"It's just another example of a lack
OL,14,Fof communication and, for some unknown
OL,15,Freason, the consumer, the customer,
OL,16,Fthe small person is then getting
OL,17,Fsqueezed," Tyler explained.
