OL,3,CBanks disputing Blue Islands refund
OL,4,Cpayments, experts claim
OL,6,F"I appreciate financial hardships and
OL,7,Fthe processes they're going through,
OL,8,Fbut I assumed that once it was paid
OL,9,Fout, I'm covered by rights, especially
OL,10,Fwith a credit card.
OL,12,F"I thought it was all done and dusted,
OL,13,Fso to now hear nothing from Blue
OL,14,FIslands and nothing else communicated,
OL,15,Fapart from through the banks, I was
OL,16,Fthinking, 'What's going on?'"
OL,18,FOften, Channel Island bank accounts
OL,19,Fcontain the same terms as those
OL,20,Fcovered by UK consumer credit laws.
