OL,3,CBanks disputing Blue Islands refund
OL,4,Cpayments, experts claim
OL,6,FThese state that credit card providers
OL,7,Fcompensate customers who have bought a
OL,8,Fservice from a company which has
OL,9,Fcollapsed, if its value was more than
OL,10,F#100.
OL,12,FInsolvency expert Adrian Rabet says it
OL,13,Fis not possible that Blue Islands, or
OL,14,Fits liquidators, Ernst & Young, are
OL,15,Fchallenging any customer claims.
OL,17,F"The dispute is between the credit
OL,18,Fcard company or debit card company and
OL,19,Fthe consumer. It's got nothing to do
OL,20,Fwith the liquidation," Mr Rabet told
OL,21,FITV News.
