OL,3,CBanks disputing Blue Islands refund
OL,4,Cpayments, experts claim
OL,6,F"There should be no problem because
OL,7,Fthe CAA released a statement saying
OL,8,Fwhat the situation was with Blue
OL,9,FIslands, that it had ceased trading.
OL,11,F"As long as you'd put in a proper
OL,12,Fclaim to your credit card company or
OL,13,Fyour debit card company with the link
OL,14,Fto that statement from the CAA, along
OL,15,Fwith the proof of your payment, there
OL,16,Fshouldn't be a problem."
