OL,3,CBanks disputing Blue Islands refund
OL,4,Cpayments, experts claim
OL,6,FIn a statement, Ernst & Young said:
OL,7,F"Blue Islands is insolvent and is in
OL,8,Fliquidation. The Joint Liquidators are
OL,9,FStuart Gardner, Dan Edkins and Simon
OL,10,FEdel of Ernst & Young LLP.
OL,12,F"Neither Blue Islands, the Joint
OL,13,FLiquidators, their staff, nor Ernst &
OL,14,FYoung LLP have challenged any refunds
OL,15,Ffrom any card providers."
OL,17,FITV Channel has approached several
OL,18,Fbanks, but none of them have confirmed
OL,19,Fthe exact reason for these particular
OL,20,Frefund disputes.
